## ğŸ“– About the App  
Employee Tracker CLI is a **content management system (CMS)** designed for business owners to **view, add, and update** company employee records through an intuitive command-line interface.  

### **Features:**  
- ğŸ“Œ **View All Departments** â€“ Lists all departments and their IDs.  
- ğŸ“Œ **View All Roles** â€“ Displays job titles, salaries, and department associations.  
- ğŸ“Œ **View All Employees** â€“ Shows employee details, including role and manager.  
- ğŸ“Œ **Add New Departments, Roles, and Employees** â€“ Allows adding new company records.  
- ğŸ“Œ **Update Employee Role & Manager** â€“ Modifies existing employee data.  
- ğŸ“Œ **View Employees by Department or Manager** â€“ Filters employees accordingly.  
- ğŸ“Œ **Delete Departments, Roles, and Employees** â€“ Removes records from the database.  
- ğŸ“Œ **Budget Overview** â€“ Calculates total salary expenses per department.  

